{"tid":2388180,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以限聚令為由巡查  陳意嵐黃店撐同路人 遭五警圍攻","createTime":"2021-01-31T02:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T04:27:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dce5dfe083a63cb479449b3229a60b91c5ec677f","tid":2388180,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210131/GJG6GF5QABG6LCCLYAL3YZOAXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210131%2FGJG6GF5QABG6LCCLYAL3YZOAXY%2F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=b0e50646\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210131%2FGJG6GF5QABG6LCCLYAL3YZOAXY%2F&h=c696f676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210131/GJG6GF5QABG6LCCLYAL3YZOAXY/</a><br />\n<br />\n以限聚令為由巡查 <br />\n陳意嵐黃店撐同路人 遭五警圍攻<br />\n<br />\n現年34歲有「翻版阿嬌」之稱的混血女星陳意嵐（Tarah）為撐手足不停發聲，由於疫情演藝工作大受影響，她轉型賣口罩，近日更大搞黃色巿集支持同路人，惟前晚她於社交網貼警員現身其黃店的照片，表示警察以限聚令為由突擊巡查，更預告可能會再來，Tarah只能抱着既來之則安之的態度，還強調會堅持做下去，又勉勵同路人指︰「齊上齊落，一齊度過艱難嘅日子！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【殺出血路】黃圈生意多元化 搶攻飲食零售<br />\n<br />\n演出過電影《選老頂》及網劇《向西聞記》的女星陳意嵐，近年撐手足不停發聲表態，她於剛過去的聖誕和新年期間，於尖東南洋中心搞黃色巿集，讓檔主寄賣東西，還有意延續至農曆新年「和你宵」活動，前日開始一連三日再有開售活動，但於商場擺檔的她，卻遭到警方留難。陳意嵐前晚於facebook貼出被五名警員突擊巡查店舖的照片，並留言：「明明話等檔主收工到齊，開晒檔就影相，畀大家知有乜新檔新嘢，過嚟衝擊，點知，檔主都未等齊，就等到佢哋。放心，人冇事，繼續準備做世界冠軍。108C會繼續堅持，提供一個安全，好玩嘅地方，畀同路人好好放鬆，努力工作，齊上齊落，一齊度過艱難嘅日子。」照片中看到陳意嵐配合警方做調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WmLCaCExW-aDRN9Eo0n1FHelZQ8=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PSKFKXCNHVDJXJPLITDWVJRS6Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWmLCaCExW-aDRN9Eo0n1FHelZQ8%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPSKFKXCNHVDJXJPLITDWVJRS6Y.jpg&h=8f9909db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【前日 慘被留難】■四名軍裝警察及一名便衣前日突擊巡查店舖，更包圍陳意嵐不停詢問巿集租約幾時完結。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k0nQs5fMxkjCAZh4DmN5n8Wx2WA=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZF5TIGERMVD3RL2DDPGU2ZJM7M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk0nQs5fMxkjCAZh4DmN5n8Wx2WA%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZF5TIGERMVD3RL2DDPGU2ZJM7M.jpg&h=36575d76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方表示收到巿民投訴，指陳意嵐的店舖有人群聚集，疑違反限聚令。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FbQcg_u9VSnDBr3g0OMR_7ccMB8=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UU2UJENFIRGG3GST773ZKPD6ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFbQcg_u9VSnDBr3g0OMR_7ccMB8%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUU2UJENFIRGG3GST773ZKPD6ZE.jpg&h=4e086753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【昨日 堅持開檔】■前日遭到警方包圍的陳意嵐，昨日仍然有返到尖東巿集睇檔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f6ZPx2ssC4HerGFD1sCTiM6Cemo=/640x950/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FPGAJHVGHFGZBH63PDGU3GCYDQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff6ZPx2ssC4HerGFD1sCTiM6Cemo%3D%2F640x950%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFPGAJHVGHFGZBH63PDGU3GCYDQ.jpg&h=788d80ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有翻版阿嬌之稱的混血女星陳意嵐，曾拍攝過《選老頂》及參選過ViuTV的《美選D.n.A》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W8bPefpcOrUx367e0OPBwb2-bHM=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YETLAXCTMBCDHHTRLXZU4X7XZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW8bPefpcOrUx367e0OPBwb2-bHM%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYETLAXCTMBCDHHTRLXZU4X7XZ4.jpg&h=fb3c8d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨日有不少巿民排隊進場支持黃色巿集。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警揚言「唔排除會再嚟」<br />\n<br />\n陳意嵐昨日透過電話回覆《蘋果》表示，前日下午近5時，正當檔主陸續返來做準備，卻有四名軍裝警員及一名女便衣探員出現，陳意嵐說：「佢哋話收到巿民投訴呢度人群聚集，所以過嚟，佢哋又引用條例提醒要注意限聚。不過我哋個場好守規矩，門口有量體溫，場內又要戴口罩，如有需要都要門外排隊。阿Sir佢提醒要保持1.5米距離同二人限聚令，但我就話108C唔係食肆，員工喺店舖工作，好難話維持二人限聚，香港舖有啲細到連1.5米都冇。加上唔係食肆，大家唔除口罩，就問佢可唔可以有清晰指引，阿Sir又冇答。查實佢係咪要我哋好似食肆咁加塊板，我哋呢個算係工作處所。」<br />\n<br />\n陳意嵐又指警察建議他們要學習名店一樣，要客人排隊進場，對此她說︰「我話冇問題，因為都問咗商場，<span class=\"orange\">附近店舖都唔介意我哋客人排隊排到佢哋門口，好歡迎我哋啲客阻到佢哋喎！</span>」她又指警察不停提問這個巿集租約幾時完結，她說：「佢哋話唔排除再有投訴會再嚟，仲話一旦見到場中人，如果唔係飲嘢食嘢而除口罩嘅話，就會畀告票佢哋。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zmjklz8I7TOyjFYRyE1VcoXwMJw=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4CLRMO5SJBEDJOEGMM55KQHTLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fzmjklz8I7TOyjFYRyE1VcoXwMJw%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4CLRMO5SJBEDJOEGMM55KQHTLQ.jpg&h=d900664f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巿集內擺放了不少檔主寄賣販售的物品，包括警方前年攻進中大的明信片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8FldqrTXaafWXtXu--YJ8WybDmg=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FFTTTJMDBZDCDFODNDALERDFL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8FldqrTXaafWXtXu--YJ8WybDmg%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFFTTTJMDBZDCDFODNDALERDFL4.jpg&h=9c7d3067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳意嵐連日來於互聯網宣傳巿集，指巿集擺放了不少印章，方便同路人自製新年文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n王宗堯曾撐場抱不平<br />\n<br />\n其實王宗堯為《蘋果》主持的節目《王探黃》，日前播出的第三集中亦有介紹過這個巿集，當日王宗堯更於巿集內消費，買了不少心頭好，場內亦有同路人光顧，難怪王宗堯前晚得悉事件後於互聯網大抱不平：「佢哋真係好得閒。」<br />\n<br />\n其實陳意嵐自從為逆權運動發聲後，上年1月曾在社交網發文發相，指朋友的汽車遭淋紅油，與她在抗爭運動做急救員有關，又指曾多次被跟蹤及電話騷擾，為此她更出post強調自己不會自殺。當時陳意嵐回覆《蘋果》時表示冇得驚：「擔心就唔走咁前啦，亦唔擔心得咁多，係咪擔心就唔會發生，唔會掟落街？」她表示接二連三見到朋友出事，朋友座駕更被淋紅油：「擔心冇意義，恐懼係好冇智慧嘅人先做。」曾為藝人杜汶澤的棟篤笑設計口罩的陳意嵐，早前亦成立公司賣口罩，發揮互助精神繼續撐起黃色經濟圈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jFPtcXhyc69odjRw-8MtkG6nG90=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VCUQZJ4GFRA5VAGNZ2JT3BULOE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjFPtcXhyc69odjRw-8MtkG6nG90%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVCUQZJ4GFRA5VAGNZ2JT3BULOE.jpg&h=c6a00a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■王宗堯早前曾親自到場支持黃色巿集。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/a3WWBxCJYy9B4jMFXIDLE3aldbY=/2050x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DTWMEHU4LJFDJK6XAXAGDCIPYU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fa3WWBxCJYy9B4jMFXIDLE3aldbY%3D%2F2050x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDTWMEHU4LJFDJK6XAXAGDCIPYU.jpg&h=f051ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳意嵐（右）早前跟化學博士K Kwong（左）一同拍片測試口罩。互聯網圖片"},{"pid":"45656fba69caef49493150490a5602dcdcdae031","tid":2388180,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5298cdc321a929d04ddf8b1c033149266f553d","tid":2388180,"uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"附近店舖都唔介意我哋客人排隊排到佢哋